# Homebrew Cask Exclusions
#
# Add one cask name per line to exclude it from automatic upgrades
# These are typically packages managed by IT/MDM systems
#
# Lines starting with # are comments and will be ignored
# Empty lines are also ignored
#
# Default exclusions (already in script):
# - docker-desktop
# - visual-studio-code
# - intellij-idea
# - slack
#
# To use this file:
# 1. Copy this file to: ~/developer-scripts/config/brew/.brew-exclude-casks
# 2. Add your custom exclusions below
# 3. Remove the example entries (or uncomment if you need them)

# Example custom exclusions (remove these and add your own):
# microsoft-teams
# zoom
# google-chrome
